						               													<description>Control unique warriors and battle your friends in fast-paced dynamic combat that will put your tactical skills to the test! Krosmaster: Blast mixes tactical combat with an area control element. Charge head first or devise a trap to catch your opponent? Defeat your enemies using sheer strength or control glyphs on the map to score a strategic victory? You must choose&amp;hellip;or maybe try both at once!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Enjoy Ankama's colorful universe and unique style in this quick and fun skirmish game in which high-quality cards, game pieces and pre-painted miniatures come together a design that's as cute as it is badass! Following in the footsteps of Krosmaster Arena, Blast is played on a gorgeous map with 3D decor elements. Each new collectible miniature is a unique fighter, greatly increasing variety and replay value. With simple rules and deep tactical possibilities, Krosmaster Blast gives you epic battles on a small board!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
